- Continue to partner with key Department of War (DoW) stakeholders and Industry partners to develop, publish, and prototype
modular standards, establishing an enterprise baseline for agile, interoperable, modular high assurance cryptography.
- Continue fielding efforts to operationalize new National Security Agency (NSA) required key management and distribution
