powered antifogging solution for combat eyewear; investigate new active laser eye protection technology concepts and assess
sensory protection gaps against emerging directed energy threats; investigate innovative backing materials to reduce behind
armor blunt trauma and improve edge performance of vital torso protection; design and develop new approaches to scalable
plate protection which incorporates novel materials and processing techniques; determine the feasibility of conformal and extreme




