Title: National Leadership Command Capability Decision Support Service (NLCC DSS) - Conference Module Development                           11.583            11.654      11.742
Description: Funds will be used for the development, integration, and test activities of NLCC DSS conference modules

FY 2026 Plans:
Activities will include, but are not limited to the following:
- Continue development activities of the first of the two additional conference modules
- Continue requirement refinement and begin development of the second of the two additional conference modules
- Continue development for NC2 conference module as required for operator or cybersecurity requirements
FY 2027 Plans:
Activities will include, but are not limited to the following:
- Continue development activities of the first of the two additional conference modules
- Continue requirement refinement and begin development of the second of the two additional conference modules
- Continue development for NC2 conference module as required for operator or cybersecurity requirements
