D. Acquisition Strategy
The Strategic Mission Planning and Execution System (SMPES) program will implement Agile DevSecOps Continuous Integration/Continuous Delivery (CI/CD) to
develop and modernize software for combatant commanders; producing a secure software development environment located in existing space at Offutt AFB, NE and
other locations. Software development environment will meet classification/security regulations/criteria, which will promote competition. The program will consider the

