A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This Project matures, optimizes, and demonstrates automated, advanced multi-function sensors and integrates threat cueing capabilities for operations in full spectrum,
complex environments, for next generation manned, optionally manned, and robotic platform applications. This Project will deliver sensor payloads which provide greatly
increased situational awareness (e.g., pre-shot and hostile fire detection, threat classification) in all environments for manned and unmanned ground vehicle systems.

