developed. Additional projects have been considered in FY 2025 to bring this technology to secure DLA’s OT systems enterprise
wide.

LTR completed the Remote Surveillance Inspection pilot study which gave DLA Additive Manufacturing SMEs a blueprint on how
to utilize Augmented/Virtual Realty to perform remote inspection to streamline acceptance processes and increase the speed with
which critical parts enter the supply chain and reach the warfighter. This project build upon the previous success of the DLA Joint

